==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lubricator
<hw>Lu"bri*ca`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, lubricates.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧ <xex>Lubricator</xex> of
the fibers.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A contrivance, as an oil cup, for supplying a
lubricant to machinery.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lubricitate</ent>⟦br⟧
